<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Newsletter Subscription Confirmation</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: #333;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #e88a49;
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 40px 20px;
      }

      .section {
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .section h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        color: #e88a49;
      }

      .section p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #e88a49;
        color: #fff !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 14px 28px;
        margin-top: 24px;
        font-size: 17px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      }

      .cta-button:hover {
        background-color: #d67a39;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #fff5ee;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
      }

      .social-links a {
        color: #e88a49;
        margin: 0 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .social-links a:hover {
        color: #d67a39;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="header">
        <h2>You're Officially Subscribed!</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h1>Hey Warrior welcome aboard!</h1>
        <p>
          Thank you for subscribing to the <strong>Warrior Sol</strong> newsletter. You're now on the inside loop for everything we do — product drops, behind-the-scenes stories, exclusive offers, and more.
        </p>
        <p>
          We’re building something meaningful, and now you’re a part of it.
        </p>
        <p>
          Keep an eye on your inbox and don’t be a stranger — we might even sneak in some surprises along the way.
        </p>
     
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Follow us for the vibes</p>
        <div class="social-links">
          <a href="https://instagram.com/warriorsol">Instagram</a> |
          <a href="https://twitter.com/warriorsol">Twitter</a> |
          <a href="https://facebook.com/warriorsol">Facebook</a>
        </div>
        <p>© 2025 Warrior Sol. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
